We have lately switched from Confluence 3.4.9 to Confluence 4.1.7, and have noticed, that the display of user names has changed. In the past, it was {{prename surname}}, now it is {{surname, prename}}. This is sometimes irritating, and reads not really well when you write something down in a protocol or so.

There should be a configuration where you can state how a user should be displayed.
